{"url":"http://www.miyazaki-group.com/recruiting/","html":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"ja\">\n<head>\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-G41M5YF4VE\"></script>\n<script>\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-G41M5YF4VE');\n</script>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>リクルーティング | 株式会社宮崎商店</title>\n  <meta name=\"description\" content=\"岩手の地元に密着70年。宮崎商店のホームページようこそ。\">\n  <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1.0,minimum-scale=1.0,user-scalable=no\">\n  <meta name=\"format-detection\" content=\"telephone=no\">\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/assets/css/style.min.css\">\n  <link href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Poppins:400,600,700\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n</head>\n<body class=\"l-recruiting\">\n  <div class=\"l-wrapper l-header__overlay\">\n\n    <header class=\"l-header\">\n      <div class=\"l-header__inner\">\n        <div class=\"l-header__head\">\n          <p class=\"l-header__logo\">\n            <a href=\"/\">\n              <img src=\"/assets/images/common/logo_corp_header.png\" alt=\"宮崎商店\">\n            </a>\n          </p>\n          <div class=\"l-header__nav-icon js-gnav-toggle\">\n            <span></span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n\n        <nav class=\"l-header__body js-gnav-list\">\n          <ul class=\"l-header__list\">\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--01\" href=\"/recruiting/\">リクルーティング</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--02\" href=\"/business/\">事業案内</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--03\" href=\"/company/\">会社案内</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--04\" href=\"https://www.talent-clip.jp/miyazaki-group/\" target=\"_blank\">採用情報</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item\">\n              <a class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--05\" href=\"/contact/\">お問い合わせ</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-header__item l-header-sub\">\n              <span class=\"l-header__link l-header__link--fb js-fb-toggle\">Facebook</span>\n              <ul class=\"l-header-sub__list\">\n                <li class=\"l-header-sub__item\">\n                  <a class=\"l-header-sub__link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E5%AE%AE%E5%B4%8E%E5%95%86%E5%BA%97-2062845797276368/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook 宮崎商店</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"l-header-sub__item\">\n                  <a class=\"l-header-sub__link\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/spasentoyukkomorioka/\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook ゆっこ盛岡</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"l-header-sub__item is-no-link\">\n                  <a class=\"l-header-sub__link\">COMING SOON !</a>\n                </li>\n              </ul>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n    </header>\n\n\n    <section class=\"l-main\">\n\n      <div class=\"c-breadcrumb\">\n        <div class=\"c-inner\">\n          <ul class=\"c-breadcrumb__list\">\n            <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__item\"><a href=\"/\">HOME</a></li>\n            <li class=\"c-breadcrumb__item\">リクルーティング</li>\n          </ul>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"l-contents\">\n        <section class=\"l-contents__box\">\n          <div class=\"l-contents__head\">\n            <div class=\"c-page-category\">\n              <p class=\"c-page-category__icon\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/common/icon_page_recruiting.png\" alt=\"\">\n              </p>\n              <p class=\"c-page-category__txt\">RECRUITING</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"c-hdg-lv1\">\n              <h1 class=\"c-hdg-lv1__txt\">リクルーティング</h1>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n\n          <div class=\"l-contents__body\">\n\n            <section class=\"c-section\">\n              <div class=\"c-hdg-lv2\">\n                <h2 class=\"c-hdg-lv2__txt\">すべての社員が成長できる場に</h2>\n              </div>\n              <p>前向きに仕事に取り組むことで、スキルを磨き、人間力を磨き、自分の可能性をどんどん広げていってほしい。<br>\n                そんな思いから、宮崎商店では社員全員のスキルアップ、キャリアアップをサポートしています。\n              </p>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"c-section\">\n              <nav class=\"p-recruiting-nav\">\n                <ul class=\"p-recruiting-nav__list\">\n                  <li class=\"p-recruiting-nav__item p-recruiting-nav__item--navy\">\n                    <a class=\"p-recruiting-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/01.html\">\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_img_01.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__txt\">\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__num\">\n                          <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_txt_01.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </p>\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__name\">磯島　実<br class=\"pc-hidden\"><span class=\"p-recruiting-nav__en\">Minoru Isojima</span></p>\n                      </div>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-recruiting-nav__item p-recruiting-nav__item--red\">\n                    <a class=\"p-recruiting-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/02.html\">\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_img_02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__txt\">\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__num\">\n                          <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_txt_02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </p>\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__name\">三浦　圧次<br class=\"pc-hidden\"><span class=\"p-recruiting-nav__en\">Atsushi Miura</span></p>\n                      </div>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-recruiting-nav__item p-recruiting-nav__item--red\">\n                    <a class=\"p-recruiting-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/03.html\">\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_img_03.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__txt\">\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__num\">\n                          <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_txt_03.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </p>\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__name\">樋口　智一<br class=\"pc-hidden\"><span class=\"p-recruiting-nav__en\">Tomokazu Higuchi</span></p>\n                      </div>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-recruiting-nav__item p-recruiting-nav__item--green\">\n                    <a class=\"p-recruiting-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/04.html\">\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_img_04.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__txt\">\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__num\">\n                          <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_txt_04.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </p>\n                         <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__name\">荒澤　雄大<br class=\"pc-hidden\"><span class=\"p-recruiting-nav__en\">Yudai Arasawa</span></p>\n                      </div>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n                  <li class=\"p-recruiting-nav__item p-recruiting-nav__item--green\">\n                    <a class=\"p-recruiting-nav__link\" href=\"/recruiting/staff/05.html\">\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__icon\">\n                        <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_img_05.png\" alt=\"\">\n                      </div>\n                      <div class=\"p-recruiting-nav__txt\">\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__num\">\n                          <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/nav_txt_05.png\" alt=\"\">\n                        </p>\n                        <p class=\"p-recruiting-nav__name\">長谷川　牧子<br class=\"pc-hidden\"><span class=\"p-recruiting-nav__en\">Makiko Hasegawa</span></p>\n                      </div>\n                    </a>\n                  </li>\n\n                </ul>\n              </nav>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"p-recruiting__box p-recruiting__box--01 p-recruiting-point\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruiting__txt\">\n                <h3 class=\"p-recruiting__hdg\">POINT.001</h3>\n                <p class=\"p-recruiting__lead\">学び合い、成長し合える環境がある</p>\n                <p class=\"p-recruiting__desc\">職場のリーダーである管理職全員が「コーチング研修」を受講。部下であるスタッフ一人一人の自己実現や目標達成をサポートし、導くためのスキルを身につけることで「学び合い、成長し合える職場」づくりを実現しています。</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruiting__img\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/point_01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n              </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"p-recruiting__box p-recruiting__box--02 p-recruiting-point\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruiting__txt\">\n                <h3 class=\"p-recruiting__hdg\">POINT.002</h3>\n                <p class=\"p-recruiting__lead\">研修や資格取得でスキルアップできる</p>\n                <p class=\"p-recruiting__desc\">社会人に必要なマナーや心構えを学ぶ研修があったり、資格を取得するための講座や受験費用を会社が負担するなど、社員のスキルアップを全面的にバックアップ。「なりたい自分」に向かって挑戦し、成長できる環境を整えています。</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruiting__img\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/point_02.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n              </div>\n            </section>\n\n            <section class=\"p-recruiting__box p-recruiting__box--03 p-recruiting-point\">\n              <div class=\"p-recruiting__txt\">\n                <h3 class=\"p-recruiting__hdg\">POINT.003</h3>\n                <p class=\"p-recruiting__lead\">成長するほど活躍の場が広がる、深まる</p>\n                <p class=\"p-recruiting__desc\">積み重ねた経験やスキル、本人の希望や特性を考慮しながら、ステップアップ、キャリアアップの機会を設けています。ひとつの仕事を極めるのもすごいし、幅広い分野で活躍するのもかっこいい。あなたの頑張りが未来を拓きます。</p>\n              </div>\n              <div class=\"p-recruiting__img\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/point_03.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n              </div>\n            </section>\n\n\n            <section class=\"p-recruiting__box p-recruiting__box--04 p-recruiting-step\">\n              <h3 class=\"p-recruiting-step__hero\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/step_01.jpg\" alt=\"\">\n              </h3>\n\n              <section>\n                <h4 class=\"p-recruiting-step__hdg\">各事業別資格取得ステップ</h4>\n\n                <section class=\"p-recruiting-step__box\">\n                  <h5 class=\"p-recruiting-step__hdg-sub\">カーライフ事業</h5>\n                  <p>\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/step_02.png\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                </section>\n\n                <section class=\"p-recruiting-step__box\">\n                  <h5 class=\"p-recruiting-step__hdg-sub\">ホームエネルギー事業</h5>\n                  <p>\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/step_03.png\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                </section>\n\n                <section class=\"p-recruiting-step__box\">\n                  <h5 class=\"p-recruiting-step__hdg-sub\">エンターテイメント事業</h5>\n                  <p>\n                    <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/step_04.png\" alt=\"\">\n                  </p>\n                </section>\n              </section>\n            </section>\n\n\n            <section class=\"c-sention c-sention--over c-message\">\n              <div class=\"c-message__left\">\n                <h2 class=\"c-message__hdg c-message__hdg--gray\">「宮崎商店」というフィールドで、<br class=\"sp-hidden\">可能性を広げてほしい</h2>\n                <p class=\"c-message__txt\">当社では、『人材の育成が最も重要である事を認識しよう』を経営バリュー第6に掲げているとおり、社員のみなさんの可能性を広げ、能力を引き出すためのサポートを惜しみません。<br>\n                  宮崎商店というフィールドでいろいろなことにチャレンジし、人として、社会人としてのスキルや魅力を磨き、豊かな人生を歩んで行ってほしいと思っております。\n                </p>\n                <p class=\"c-message__txt u-ta-right\">代表取締役社長　佐々木 太介</p>\n              </div>\n\n              <div class=\"c-message__portrait\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/portrait_02_sp.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"pc-hidden\">\n                <img src=\"/assets/images/recruiting/portrait_02_pc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"sp-hidden\">\n              </div>\n            </section>\n\n          </div>\n        </section>\n\n\n      </div><!-- /.l-contents -->\n\n    </section><!-- /.l-main -->\n\n\n    <footer class=\"l-footer\">\n      <div class=\"l-footer__links\">\n        <p class=\"l-footer-links__corporate-logo\">\n          <a href=\"/\">\n            <img src=\"/assets/images/common/logo_corp_footer.png\" alt=\"宮崎商店 Miyazaki Syoten Ltd.\">\n          </a>\n        </p>\n        <nav class=\"l-footer-links__nav\">\n          <ul class=\"l-footer-links__list\">\n            <li class=\"l-footer-links__item\">\n              <a href=\"/privacy/\">個人情報保護方針</a>\n            </li>\n            <li class=\"l-footer-links__item\">\n              <a href=\"/sitemap.html\">サイトマップ</a>\n            </li>\n          </ul>\n        </nav>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"l-footer__copyright\">\n        <p>\n          Copyright 2017(c) Miyazaki Syoten Co.,Ltd. All Rights Reserved.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </footer>\n\n\n  </div><!-- /.l-wrapper -->\n\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/jquery-3.1.1.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/jquery.easing.1.3.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/slick.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/jquery.fadethis.min.js\"></script>\n  <script src=\"/assets/js/common.js\"></script>\n\n</body>\n</html>","finalUrl":"http://www.miyazaki-group.com/recruiting/","rendered":false,"_cachedAt":"2026-06-17T23:28:46.659Z"}